description:
Part 32 of 40. Do you feel discouraged, lost, or helpless? If so, this unique 3-part series is JUST FOR YOU. Inside the pages of an ancient book (the Bible) you will discover how Jesus Christ (the Savior of the world) gave hope to three very different people: A leper, and outcast woman, and a demon-possessed man. Believe it or not, Jesus can help you, too. https://youtu.be/bS2k24PkOZY
